val.title: Dublin Commons

details.Application Type: Site Development Review Permit, Vesting Tentative Tract Map, and Development Agreement.

Applicant.name: Mario Tjia, Director Hines Interests, LP
Applicant.address: 101 California Street, Ste. 100 San Francisco, CA 94111

val.description: The Dublin Commons project is the redevelopment of the Dublin Plaza Shopping Center as part of implementing the Downtown Dublin Preferred Vision. Dublin Commons is a mixed-use project of up to 275,000 SF of retail (consisting of 155,000 SF of new retail and , 120,000 SF of existing retail), 535,000 SF of Research and Development (Life Science), 1,510 multifamily residential units and a new Town Square/park. The project entitlements include a Site Development Review Permit, Tentative Tract Map, amendment to the Downtown Dublin Specific Plan and a Development Agreement.
